  "title": "Field Service Engineer ( Junior / Training Provided ) - 5days | Tampines",
  "description": "<p><strong>Field Service Assistant Engineer (FSAE)</strong><br />Working Salary : $2500 - $3000 + $140 Allowance<br />Working Days: Mon - Fri | 8.30 - 5.30pm<br />Working Location: Tampines<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Providing technical support to field service teams</li><li>Supporting Factory Acceptance test and Site Acceptance test</li><li>Maintaining accurate and reliable service tool inventory</li><li>Completing service documentation is completed in proper format and by due dates- this includes items such as timesheets, service/repair reports, follow ups, daily logs, expenses, etc.</li><li>Ensuring proper storage of engineering documentation- drawings, version history, scope documents, RFI's Job</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Instrumentation / CPT / Electronics / Mechatronic Engineering</li><li>Training Provided</li></ul><p><strong>Tee Xin Li Reg No: R24121619</strong><br /><strong>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
